---
import AboutHeroImage from '../assets/blog-placeholder-about.jpg';
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About UNIQM"
	description="Learn about UNIQM's aerial storytelling services for real estate"
	pubDate={new Date('January 01 2024')}
	heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
>
	<p>
		UNIQM is a professional aerial media company specializing in drone photography and videography for the real estate industry. Based in the Netherlands, we combine cutting-edge drone technology with creative storytelling to deliver exceptional visual content that showcases properties in their best light.
	</p>

	<p>
		Our mission is to revolutionize how properties are presented through the power of aerial perspective. We work with real estate agents, developers, and property owners to create compelling visual narratives that engage buyers and highlight key features that ground-level photography simply cannot capture.
	</p>

	<p>
		With years of experience in aerial cinematography and a deep understanding of the real estate market, UNIQM brings a unique blend of technical expertise and creative vision to every project. Our team is equipped with state-of-the-art drone equipment and post-production facilities to ensure the highest quality output.
	</p>

	<p>
		Whether it's capturing expansive property views, showcasing surrounding neighborhoods, or creating immersive virtual tours, we deliver content that makes properties stand out in a competitive market. Our services are designed to complement marketing efforts and help clients achieve their sales goals.
	</p>

	<p>
		Located in the Netherlands, we proudly serve real estate professionals throughout the country and beyond. We're committed to delivering reliable, professional service with a focus on quality, creativity, and client satisfaction.
	</p>
</Layout>
